Package org.mybatis.maven.mvnmigrate

Contains myBatis migration command implementation for this plugin.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BootstrapCommandMojo
    Goal which execute the ibatis migration bootstrap command.
    CheckCommandMojo
    Goal which check the presence of pending migration.
    DownCommandMojo
    Goal which execute the ibatis migration status command.
    HelpMojo
    Display help information on migrations-maven-plugin.
    Call mvn migration:help -Ddetail=true -Dgoal=<goal-name> to display parameter details.
    InitCommandMojo
    Goal which executes the MyBatis migration init command.
    NewCommandMojo
    Goal which executes the ibatis migration new command.
    PendingCommandMojo
    Goal which execute the ibatis migration pending command.
    ScriptCommandMojo
    Goal which executes the ibatis migration script command.
    StatusCommandMojo
    Goal which execute the ibatis migration status command.
    UpCommandMojo
    Goal which execute the ibatis migration status command.
    VersionCommandMojo
    Goal which execute the ibatis migration version command.
